OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FThe MSP bidding to give terminally ill
OL,7,FScots the right to request help to die
OL,8,Fhas made a last ditch plea to MSPs at
OL,9,FHolyrood to pass assisted dying
OL,10,Flegislation.
OL,12,FLiam McArthur insists the proposals he
OL,13,Fhas developed would be "the toughest
OL,14,Fand most comprehensively safeguarded
OL,15,Fassisted dying Bill in the world".
OL,17,FHe will meet campaigners who back a
OL,18,Fchange of the law outside Holyrood on
OL,19,FTuesday ahead of his Bill facing its
OL,20,Ffinal, crucial vote at 10pm.
OL,26,@uD@XOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FBut appealing to fellow MSPs, who will
OL,7,Fdecide if the proposals become law,
OL,8,Fthe Liberal Democrat MSP insisted:
OL,9,F"This is now the toughest and most
OL,10,Fcomprehensively safeguarded assisted
OL,11,Fdying bill in the world.
OL,13,F"If you believe that dying people
OL,14,Fshould not have to suffer against
OL,15,Ftheir will and you have heard, like I
OL,16,Fhave, of the many instances where they
OL,17,Fhave been simply failed by the lack of
OL,18,Fcompassion and safety in our current
OL,19,Flaw, you now have to back this Bill.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,F"It is time to look terminally ill
OL,7,FScots in the eye and make this change."
OL,9,FOpponents of the legislation, who fear
OL,10,Fthe impact of assisted dying on the
OL,11,Fdisabled and other vulnerable groups,
OL,12,Fwill also be gathering outside the
OL,13,FScottish Parliament in advance of the
OL,14,Fknife-edge vote.
OL,16,FIt comes after MSPs made changes to
OL,17,Fthe Assisted Dying for Terminally Ill
OL,18,FAdults (Scotland) Bill in four lengthy
OL,19,Fsessions at Holyrood last week, with a
OL,20,Ftotal of 175 changes to the
OL,21,Flegislation agreed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FMr McArthur said: "When I launched
OL,7,Fthis Bill, I said that I wanted to
OL,8,Fdeliver a robust and well safeguarded
OL,9,Flaw that would give terminally ill
OL,10,FScots with mental capacity the choice
OL,11,Fof an assisted death if they wanted
OL,12,Fone.
OL,14,F"After five years of development,
OL,15,Fconsultation, revision and amendment,
OL,16,Fthat Bill now sits before Parliament."
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FHis proposals would allow for Scots to
OL,7,Flegally seek help to end their life,
OL,8,Fwith the Bill requiring two doctors
OL,9,Fwould have both to confirm that a
OL,10,Fperson in terminally ill and has the
OL,11,Fmental capacity to make such a request.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a change introduced last
OL,14,Fweek would mean that people should be
OL,15,F"reasonably expected" to have six
OL,16,Fmonths to live or less before they
OL,17,Fwould be eligible for an assisted
OL,18,Fdeath.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FMr McArthur added: "MSPs have added
OL,7,Fdetailed amendments on coercion,
OL,8,Fprognosis and protection of vulnerable
OL,9,Fgroups and there are cast iron
OL,10,Fprotections for healthcare
OL,11,Fprofessionals ready to go."
OL,13,FMSPs will be given a free vote when
OL,14,Fthe legislation comes before later
OL,15,Ftonight.
OL,26,@nD@TOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FBut with groups in the medical
OL,7,Fprofession ` including the Royal
OL,8,FCollege of Psychiatrists (RCS) and
OL,9,FRoyal Pharmaceutical Society ` having
OL,10,Fmade clear their opposition the Bill,
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Kate Forbes
OL,12,Furged MSPs to consider their views.
OL,14,FMs Forbes said: "I will vote against
OL,15,FAssisted Dying because the Bill is now
OL,16,Friskier and less safe after MSPs
OL,17,Frejected critical safeguards and
OL,18,Foutsourced essential protections for
OL,19,Fdoctors to the UK Government.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,F"Doctors, psychiatrists, pharmacists
OL,7,Fand palliative care specialists ` the
OL,8,Fpeople who would be tasked with
OL,9,Fimplementing this ` are asking us not
OL,10,Fto do it.
OL,12,F"These are the people on the front
OL,13,Fline of compassion in Scotland, the
OL,14,Fpeople who have dedicated their lives
OL,15,Fand careers to helping people in life
OL,16,Fand in death. They think this Bill is
OL,17,Funsafe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FShe added: "I know MSPs are motivated
OL,7,Fby compassion, and so we should heed
OL,8,Finterventions from doctors and nurses
OL,9,Fwhose whole careers are dedicated to
OL,10,Fcaring for us."
OL,12,FThis is the third time MSPs have
OL,13,Fconsidered legislation on assisted
OL,14,Fdying, with two previous attempts
OL,15,Fhaving failed at their first vote.
OL,17,FDr Gordon Macdonald, chief executive
OL,18,Fof campaign group Care Not Killing,
OL,19,Finsisted such legislation "offers a
OL,20,Fvision of the future which has no
OL,21,Fplace in a caring Scottish society".
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@OO]{D@[OU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FHe added: "Vulnerable people who are
OL,7,Fsick, elderly or disabled, can so
OL,8,Feasily feel pressure, whether real or
OL,9,Fimagined, to end their lives so as not
OL,10,Fto be a burden on others.
OL,12,F"Parliament's first responsibility is
OL,13,Fto protect its most vulnerable
OL,14,Fcitizens from exploitation and abuse
OL,15,Fby those who may have a financial or
OL,16,Femotional interest in their deaths."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,FHowever, Emma Cooper, convener of
OL,7,Fcampaign group, Friends at the End
OL,8,F(Fate), said: "The vast majority of
OL,9,Fpeople in every single constituency
OL,10,Facross Scotland are asking for
OL,11,Fassisted dying to be made available to
OL,12,Fthose who are mentally competent and
OL,13,Fin the last six months of their life.
OL,15,F"We cannot deny those who are going to
OL,16,Fdie the right to choose. It is simply
OL,17,Fa misconception that pain relief can
OL,18,Falleviate the suffering of all
OL,19,Fconditions at the end of life.
OL,26,@pD@OOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773734676
OL,3,CLast ditch pleas made to MSPs before
OL,4,CHolyrood votes on Assisted Dying Bill
OL,6,F"Passing this Bill is the right thing
OL,7,Fto do, the only compassionate
OL,8,Fdecision."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
